2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper deals with secure communication and proposes a scheme for generating a shared secret key, which falls under the scope of cryptography and security.
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with communication channels and feedback, which are relevant to social and information networks.
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with communication channels and feedback, which are relevant to networking and internet architecture.
